room_title: Escape room "A Strange Case" by Room With a Clue in Honolulu
room_address: 1130 N Nimitz Hwy, Suite B295, Honolulu, HI 96817
room_description: A mystery has baffled the town since the mid 1980's, when several children went missing. Bizarre circumstances, weird noises, and odd powers were present in the town. The cases remained unsolved. One boy's mother dedicated her life to finding out what happened. You're here at his childhood home to look for clues that can save him.
